</date><respStmt><resp>IDP</resp></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>IIIspc</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><choice><corr>Παυσανίας</corr><sic>παυσσανιας</sic></choice> Ἡρακλείδῃ τῶι ἀδελφῶι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>οἴομαι τὸν ἀδελφὸν Σαραπάμμωνα μεταδεδωκέναι <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>μειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="3"/>δι᾽ ἣν αἰτίαν κατῆλθον εἰς Ἀλεξάνδρειαν, φθάνω δὲ <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>μειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>πρότερον γεγραφηκὼς περὶ τοῦ <choice><corr>μικροῦ</corr><sic>μεικρου</sic></choice> Παυσανίου 

    <lb n="5"/>ὡς εἰς λεγιῶνα <choice><corr>στρατευσαμένου</corr><sic>στρατευσαμενον</sic></choice>. ὡς οὖν ἐβουλήθη μη-

    <lb n="6"/>κέτι εἰς λεγιῶναν ἀλλὰ εἰς εἶλαν, μαθὼν ἀναγκαίως ἔσχον 

    <lb n="7"/>πρὸς αὐτὸν καταντῆσαι, καίτοι μὴ βουλόμενος. δεηθεὶς 

    <lb n="8"/>οὖν πολλὰ ὑπὸ τῆς μητρὸς αὐτοῦ καὶ τῆς ἀδελφῆς εἰς Κό-

    <lb n="9"/>πτον αὐτὸν μετενεγκεῖν, κατελθὼν εἰς Ἀλεξάνδρειαν 

    <lb n="10"/>πολλαῖς ἀφορμαῖς ἐχρησάμην ἄχρι οὗ <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">υ</del> μετενέχθη 

    <lb n="11"/>εἰς τὴν ἐν Κόπτῳ εἶλαν. ἐπιθυμῶν οὖν πρὸς <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μᾶς 

    <lb n="12"/>τῷ ἀν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">απλ</unclear>ό<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῳ</unclear> καταντῆσαι περιεκλείσθημεν ἀπὸ τοῦ 

    <lb n="13"/>δοθέντος <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῷ παι</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δί</unclear>ῳ ὑπὸ τοῦ λαμπροτάτου ἡγεμόνος 

    <lb n="14"/>κο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μ</unclear>εά<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ου,</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αὶ δ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ι</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὰ τ</supplied>αύτην τὴν αἰτίαν οὐκ <choice><corr>ἴσχυσα</corr><sic>εισχυσα</sic></choice> πρὸς 

    <lb n="15"/><hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied>ᾶς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κ</supplied>αταντῆσαι. θεῶν οὖν βουλομένων πρὸς τὴν 

    <lb n="16"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἑορ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>ὴ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῶ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> Ἀμεσυσίων πειράσομαι πρὸς <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μᾶς γενέ-

    <lb n="17"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σθ</supplied>αι. μ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ελη</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σάτ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ω</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σο</unclear>ι οὖν, ἄδελφε, περὶ τοῦ γράμματος τῆς 

    <lb n="18"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὑ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πο</unclear>θήκ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ης ὥ</supplied>στε αὐτὸ ἀπαρτισθῆναι καθὼς ἔθος ἐστίν.

    <lb n="19"/>παρακαλῶ οὖ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν,</supplied> ἄδελφε, γράψαι μοι περὶ τῆς ὑμῶν σω-

    <lb n="20"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ηρίας, ἐπεὶ ἤκουσα ἐν τῇ Ἀντινόου ὅτι παρ᾽ <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>μειν</sic></choice> λοιμὸς 

    <lb n="21"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐγ</supplied>ένετο. μὴ οὖν ἀμελήσῃς, <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να <choice><corr>καὶ ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> περὶ <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μῶν εὐθυ-

    <lb n="22"/>μότερον διάξω. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="r,ms" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="23"/>ἀσπάζου πολλὰ τὴν κυρίαν μου μητέρα καὶ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τὴν ἀδελ</supplied>-

    <lb n="24"/>φήν μου καὶ τὰ ἀβάσκαντα ἡμῶν παιδ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ία. ἀσπά</supplied>ζε-

    <lb n="25"/>ται <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μᾶς Παυσανίας. ἐρρῶσθ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αί</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear> <expan><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">εὔχ<ex cert="high">ομαι</ex></supplied></expan> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πα</unclear>ν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ικ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear>ί. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="26"/>εἰς Ὀξυρυγχείτην Ἡρα<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κλ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ί</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δῃ </supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μν</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="27"/><expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Παυσανίου ἀδελφοῦ. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.31777" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31777" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="300">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.31777" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.31777" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">14</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1666</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">31777</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">14</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1666</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;14;1666" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31777" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">151</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.31777" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31777" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Sel. Pap. I 149</bibl><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Tibiletti, Lettere private 3</bibl></listBibl></div><di